A sleek black fitness watch with a glowing display rests on weathered wooden planks beside well-worn running shoes, morning dew droplets catching golden sunrise light, shallow depth of field creating dreamy bokeh in the background of a misty forest trail, photorealistic style with rich warm tones and crisp detail on the watch face showing abstract fitness metrics, the composition suggests anticipation and the quiet moment before a workout begins, atmospheric fog weaving between distant trees.
